action.label: POST_A_CustomerCompany
action.name: POST_A_CustomerCompany
action.description: Creates new company code data linked to the customer. Assigns company code data to a customer. A customer can be assigned to multiple company records.

action.label: POST_A_BusinessPartnerRole
action.name: POST_A_BusinessPartnerRole
action.description: Creates a new role for an existing business partner. Adds a new role to the existing business partner record with role and validity details.

action.label: GET_A_BusinessPartnerRole
